{"tid":1079651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維尼訪法豪撒400億歐元銀彈 遭誤稱中華民國總統","createTime":"2019-03-27T05:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T10:01:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c90cc1939996c1f7746259ab6116a44b5f704be6","tid":1079651,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"中國國家主席習近平訪問法國狂撒錢，簽署價值400億歐元的多項雙邊經貿協議，而法國當局也對這位有錢的中國大爺熱情招呼，數條交通路線因此變動。不料，其中之一的巴黎地鐵出包，竟稱習近平為「中華民國總統」（Pr&eacute;sident de la R&eacute;publique de Chine），遭網友指正「中華民國是台灣，中華人民共和國是中國」。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在尼斯接受法國總統馬克宏（Emmanuel Macron）設宴款待後，第2天即驅車前往巴黎，當地部分路線及車站略有更動或暫時封閉。其中巴黎地鐵6號線（Ligne 6 RATP）在官方推特公告「在中華民國總統訪問之後，將於3月26日星期二15:30左右重新開放」，就把習近平當成「中華民國總統」。<br />\n<br />\n此一錯誤被推特上網友發現，紛紛留言。Cheng Kong表示「中華民國是台灣，中華人民共和國是中國」，Anubis75則解釋「中華民國是另一回事」，SSF Chaotic指正說習近平是「中國共和國的總統」。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎地鐵6號線的稱呼錯誤，一直到台灣時間26日上午7時都沒有更正。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，法國總統馬克宏則在臉書放上與「Pr&eacute;sident de la R&eacute;publiquepopulaire de Chine」（中華人民共和國主席）習近平一起召開記者會的直播影片。這次習近平訪法簽署多項雙邊經貿協議，包括同意購買300架法國空中巴士，總值高達400 億歐元，6小時吸引將近5萬人次觀看。雖然有人叫好，直呼「法國萬歲、中國萬歲」，卻也有不少臉友表達憤怒，Pierrick Thev留言提醒「法國越來越接近中國，我們須避開法國也有天安門」；Yamina Mya則痛批「獨裁者」，Alain Andrieux留言「請習近平帶走我們這個沒腦子的法西斯傀儡吧」！還有Chungpo Rigtselwa警告「不要相信中國......要小心中國」。"},{"pid":"f7a98567f61872f0f0f1109aacaa110bea234e3f","tid":1079651,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"一個中國原則下<br />\nla r&eacute;publique de chine = la r&eacute;publique populaire de chine = la chine"},{"pid":"ae50b3b0a93a8129721dde2aac814d8169fb1ec6","tid":1079651,"uid":45477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f965e0ecf9a33b3fc45f435cfad389534bc125","tid":1079651,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"法國佬都幾古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7372110c698f00fc5e258fac3a4b3c2724d304","tid":1079651,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70f965e0ecf9a33b3fc45f435cfad389534bc125","tid":1079651,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"法國佬都幾古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"玩開革命國家都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99479aeb3f7c93aa50106f28f9156772566387c","tid":1079651,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"固意的錯誤，維尼熊真係去到邊都比人玩鳩"},{"pid":"e0bbee6bf7671bf0ee06724c64fe7a30f7c198e1","tid":1079651,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:57:37.000Z","msg":"網友你分到咁清楚係咪搞台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc6873cf26e5fa6abe07727583da427252462c4","tid":1079651,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0bbee6bf7671bf0ee06724c64fe7a30f7c198e1","tid":1079651,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:57:37.000Z","msg":"網友你分到咁清楚係咪搞台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"鬼拍後尾枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cab141e73326bfd14003738314aa63e35794110","tid":1079651,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b7372110c698f00fc5e258fac3a4b3c2724d304","tid":1079651,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70f965e0ecf9a33b3fc45f435cfad389534bc125","tid":1079651,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"法國佬都幾古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"玩開革命國家都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}